results.title: The Hunger Part 1
results.description: Detective Garrett investigates a series of murders where all of the victims have puncture marks on their backs and their bodies have been stripped clean of adrenaline; Eddie seeks forgiveness from a priest for past sins; Peter, May and Liz gather at the hospital to watch the bandages being taken off of the face of the badly injured and mostly comatose Flash Thompson;  Spidey gets into a brawl with Venom, only to find out that the symbiote is traveling around without its human host.

results.title: MMIII, Anno Morionis (Year of the Madman, 2003)
results.description: A tale of the future and the legacy of Nathan Summers.

results.title: The Low Budget Action Movie
results.description: Over Kashmir, Nathan runs into some very bad men.  With his newfound peace, Nathan proceeds to make a difference---without fighting.  After hearing about the word "Askani" being said by a stranger, Nathan finds Blaquesmith, who now has a secret.  A secret about himself and his agenda...

results.title: The Askani Way
results.description: Nathan makes a decision to be his own man.  But at what price?  Geo becomes a hero in the conclusion to this storyline.  Plus, Jordan and Dragonfly catch a break.

results.title: The Siege of Saint Lenin
results.description: While Nathan, Geo, Magdalena, and the priest hide out, Magdalena's mother is tortured.  Nathan realizes that the girl he saved has changed.  During his "discussion" with Geo, Nathan makes a decision.

results.title: Geo-logic
results.description: A character by the name of Geo beats up on Nathan because the Mob is confusing him for Nathan...all because of a metal arm.  Meanwhile, the Mob make their way to the church and all hell breaks loose.  In the process, Magdalena suffers an unfortunate fate and Nathan has to step in.

results.title: The Virgin of Krasnaya Polyana
results.description: Oleg loses the nerve to get his daughter, so Nathan goes in alone.  As Nathan approaches the church, he sees a line of sick and needy people waiting for Magdalena's touch of healing.  Nathan busts in to rescue her, but then he is bushwacked by a mysterious stranger.

results.title: Moscow Nights
results.description: Jordan and Dragonfly continue their search for Nathan's whereabouts.  Blaquesmith lets Nathan know his next mission: find a Russian girl with the power to heal.  Of course, the Russian Mafia is also after her.

results.title: The Hunger Part 2
results.description: Garrett continues his investigation into the bizarre adrenaline attacks; Venom bonds with Eddie again and continues to use and abuse his human host; Spidey tracks down Detective Garrett and fills him in on the Venom factor of his current case.

results.title: Dear Irene...
results.description: Irene is still sure that Nathan is alive even though she hasn't heard from him in two years.  After a run-in with S.H.I.E.L.D. agents, she receives proof that Nathan is still alive--a diary from Nathan.  In it, Nathan tells Irene about his search for a purpose and his reunion with an old friend.
